  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I arrived to the town of Papa.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My geography, and [INAUDIBLE], and [INAUDIBLE] with-- with this truck, which was going for supplies and so on, apparently helped me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't walk much after that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I got on a train, which was not a scheduled train, but some train which I understood is going to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And on that train, and with supply of some food which from that storage area, the Russian soldiers let me have some bread, and some dried meat, and some can of water, and so forth, I was on the train.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I wasn't alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There were town people from the neighborhood areas and so on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the train had all kind of makeshift arrangements, some of it was seating.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Some it was-- some of the people even have tickets.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I had, by the way, some Hungarian money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because one of the Russian soldier reached into his pocket and gave me a bunch of money, which I had no idea.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It looked different from the money which I used to see.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it was written in Hungarian on it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So it was some new money they printed, because the city of Budapest, and before they got to the border, a considerable time passed by.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And by then, there was some sort of government in Budapest, which we started to print money.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And life started to return apparently.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So with that money, I thought, if you need ticket, I can buy ticket.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But then I-- I heard that the whistle of the train is about to give signal that they take off, so a bunch of us were sitting on the top of wagons, just out on the top of the wagon, sitting on it.",
      "word_count": 43
    }
  ],
